-13T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"應該唔關事"},{"pid":"25d2c3937ef2a20b881ff128aa53bf7098a85682","tid":1876172,"uid":129138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:57:12.000Z","msg":"其實社會還社會，自己還自己<br />\n社會既所謂大事係大環境，同自身經歷既事比唔係咩大事"},{"pid":"4e7750bcfa7b9eb18327fcc7d37e4824cff0116e","tid":1876172,"uid":26666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"暑假後離開左但一直有留意香港既事<br />\n返到黎有時見到街上既塗鴉 用膠鏈替代既欄杆 用水泥鋪返既磚路<br />\n某啲聽唔到紅綠燈聲既馬路 冇左綠色公仔既交通燈<br />\n貼完又被撕 變得溶溶爛爛既連儂牆<br />\n然後諗返之前香港所發生既事 再睇下街上既人<br />\n感覺真係好平行時空 好唔真實 香港曾經陷入過戰爭狀態...<br />\n但我知道好多人都未能忘記<br />\n街上既殘破損毀猶如呢八個月每個香港人既損傷一樣<br />\n不論肉體定心靈上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa47fca462cd66b31279dea4ebf366de4667c4c","tid":1876172,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0542e6cb3e53a3263ada059754f55e636a3dfa1","tid":1876172,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0ca60a5de96130068dcedcb755081e3fd3ab03e","tid":1876172,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aec3bef785b565aff260aa4b87dd1a49676378b","tid":1876172,"uid":49843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:11:55.000Z","msg":"但恒指仲係狂升<br />\n香港愈差 恒指升得愈勁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:41:01.000Z","msg":"外國好似覺得示威者係制衡緊極權政府 對經濟係好事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"應該唔關事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"下原來無用嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補source先 <a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/26282/%E7%A9%86%E8%BF%AA%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E7%AE%A1%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%8F%E5%BF%97-26282/%E4%B8%BB%E6%B5%81%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%A1%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%8F%E5%BF%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F26282%2F%25E7%25A9%2586%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25BF%2597-2628